snippet.title: HERO SPOTLIGHT | DOTLER 😈
snippet.description:
Hands up if you are DOTLER’s stan 🙌🏴‍☠️

😈 DOTLER - A smart (sometimes mischievous) and fierce bruiser legend hero from Ethern Tribe, who is full of strength and magic power to be the king of an arena!

DOTLER is ready to use his powerful punch & skills to strike on the #Everfield 🔯🔥
See his skills closely in the ‘Hero Spotlight’

#Evermoon #Herospotlight #MOBA #NFT
